issue.title: [Event Hubs Trigger] Update template version
issue.body:
# Summary

The focus of these changes is to update the version of the package referenced for the current generation of the Azure SDK.  The version has been bumped to 6.0.0, with the containing folder renamed to reflect the change.

pull_request.title: Default Precompiled .NET templates to using track 2 extensions
pull_request.body:
This PR defaults all precompiled .NET templates to using track 2 Azure SDK extensions, and updates the templates accordingly.

Affected templates:
* C# CosmosDB trigger
* F# CosmosDB trigger
* C# EventGrid trigger
* F# EventGrid trigger
* C# EventHub trigger
* F# EventHub trigger
* C# Storage Queue trigger
* F# Storage Queue trigger 
* C# SendGrid Trigger
* C# ServiceBus Queue trigger
* C# ServiceBus Topic trigger
